393
00:28:21,900 --> 00:28:26,900
粉雪ね
Powder snow, huh...

394
00:28:26,900 --> 00:28:30,400
心まで白く染められたなら
If even my heart could be dyed white...

395
00:28:36,900 --> 00:28:45,900
二人の孤独を分け合うことができたのかい
...would we have been able to share our loneliness?

396
00:28:56,400 --> 00:29:01,900
僕は君の心に
I'll put my ear...

397
00:29:01,900 --> 00:29:08,100
耳を押しあてて
...to your heart

398
00:29:08,100 --> 00:29:13,400
その声のするほうへ
Towards where that voice comes from...

399
00:29:13,400 --> 00:29:19,100
スッと深くまで
...and straight down to the depths...

400
00:29:19,100 --> 00:29:22,400
下りてゆきたい
...I want to descend

401
00:29:22,400 --> 00:29:26,900
ここでもう一度会おう
Let's meet here once more

402
00:29:26,900 --> 00:29:34,900
分かり合いたいなんて
To say I want to understand each other...

403
00:29:34,900 --> 00:29:40,400
上辺を撫でていたのは僕のほう
...it was me who was just scratching the surface

404
00:29:40,400 --> 00:29:44,700
君のかじかんだ手を
Your frozen hands...

405
00:29:44,700 --> 00:29:49,900
握りしめることだけで
...just by squeezing them tightly...

406
00:29:49,900 --> 00:29:57,400
繋がってたのに
...we were connected, and yet...

407
00:29:57,400 --> 00:30:02,400
粉雪ね
Powder snow, huh...

408
00:30:02,400 --> 00:30:04,900
時に頼りなく
Sometimes unreliable...

409
00:30:03,845 --> 00:30:09,645
...ああまりにもろく... あはは...
