そんなのもありましたね。
That was a thing too, wasn't it?

661
00:51:36,825 --> 00:51:38,725
そうだ、接近カメラね、欲しかったね。
Right, I wanted a close-up camera.

662
00:51:38,725 --> 00:51:41,225
ガチ恋距離ないんですか、カメラさん？
Is there no "Gachikoi" distance, Mr. Camera Man?

663
00:51:41,225 --> 00:51:42,925
ミオのガチ恋距離ないんですか？
No Gachikoi distance for Mio?

664
00:51:43,225 --> 00:51:44,625
うちが近づいたほうがいいのかな？
Should I move closer?

665
00:51:44,825 --> 00:51:48,725
よ、どうなんだ、カメラさん？顔アップ...
Yo, what's the deal, camera man? Close-up face...

666
00:51:48,925 --> 00:51:51,525
え、それやば！え、それやば、ミオ！
Whoa, that's crazy! Whoa, that's crazy, Mio!

667
00:51:51,725 --> 00:51:53,525
みんな、見てる？
Everyone, are you watching?

668
00:51:53,725 --> 00:51:54,725
それは可愛い、ミオ。
That's so cute, Mio.

669
00:51:55,225 --> 00:51:57,725
お、近い！来た来た来た！すごい！
Oh, so close! Here it comes! Amazing!

670
00:51:57,925 --> 00:52:01,225
カメラさん。ちょ、待って、恥ずかしいので、ちょっとそんな近くに...
Mr. Camera Man. W-wait, I'm getting embarrassed, so don't get *that* close...

671
00:52:01,225 --> 00:52:03,725
そんなことない、そんなことない。待って待って、クリーム付いてた？
Not at all, not at all. Wait, wait, was there cream on you?

672
00:52:03,725 --> 00:52:08,725
見せろ見せろ、やめてやめて。サンホールも食ったろ。
Show us, show us! Stop, stop! You ate the Sunhole too, right?

673
00:52:08,925 --> 00:52:10,725
付いてない、付いてないもう。
There's nothing on me, nothing anymore.

674
00:52:10,925 --> 00:52:11,725
うふふ。
Hehe.

675
00:52:12,225 --> 00:52:14,225
サンホールも食べたミオ。
Mio, who ate the Sunhole.

676
00:52:14,225 --> 00:52:16,025
確かにサンホール食べた。結構重いね、やっぱりね。
I did indeed eat the Sunhole. It's pretty heavy, after all.

677
00:52:16,225 --> 00:52:18,725
本当だよ。みんな今のスクショしたか？ちゃんと。
True that. Did everyone get a screenshot of that? Make sure you did.

678
00:52:18,925 --> 00:52:23,025
今のはちょっとガチ恋距離っていうか、もう接触距離だよ。
That wasn't just Gachikoi distance, it was practically contact distance.

679
00:52:23,225 --> 00:52:24,725
いいじゃん、もう接触。
It's fine, contact is good.

680
00:52:24,925 --> 00:52:27,225
接触距離助かる。
Contact distance is a lifesaver.

681
00:52:27,225 --> 00:52:29,725
助からない助からない。ミオミオ！
Not really, not really. Mio-Mio!

682
00:52:29,825 --> 00:52:32,225
なんと！次で最後の曲。
And now! The next one is the last song.

683
00:52:32,425 --> 00:52:33,725
そうなんだよ。
That's right.

684
00:52:33,925 --> 00:52:35,225
やだー！
Nooo!

685
00:52:35,225 --> 00:52:39,725
延長しろ！延長しろ！わーわー！
Encore! Encore! Waa waa!

686
00:52:39,925 --> 00:52:41,225
捏ねるんじゃねー。
Don't start complaining.

687
00:52:41,725 --> 00:52:45,925
というわけでですね、えーと、ま、最後の曲なんですけれども。
And so, well, it's the last song.

688
00:52:46,125 --> 00:52:49,725
最後はね、ちょっとフブキにも一緒に歌ってもらおうかなと思って。
For the last one, I thought I'd have Fubuki sing with me.

689
00:52:49,925 --> 00:52:51,525
あ、じゃあ邪魔しない程度に。
Ah, then I'll try not to get in the way.

690
00:52:51,725 --> 00:52:55,725
合いの手をね、得意だって言ってるから。合いの手をお願いします。
She says she's good at backing chants. Please do the backing chants.

691
00:52:55,925 --> 00:52:59,725
そうですね、合いの手を。程よい合いの手を。
That's right, chants. Just the right amount of chants.

692
00:52:59,925 --> 00:53:01,225
うん。お願いします。
Yeah. Please do.

693
00:53:01,425 --> 00:53:02,225
はい！
Okay!

694
00:53:02,425 --> 00:53:04,525
というわけで皆さん、何を歌うんですか？
So, everyone, what am I going to sing?

695
00:53:04,725 --> 00:53:08,725
ちょっとね、最後の曲になりますが、喜んでくれると嬉しいです。
It's the last song, and I hope you'll enjoy it.

696
00:53:08,725 --> 00:53:11,225
ちょっと喉のあたりドキドキしますけれども。
My throat feels a bit nervous.

697
00:53:12,225 --> 00:53:16,225
最後は、「夢見る空へ」で締めたいと思います。
For the finale, I'd like to close with "Yumemiru Sora e".

698
00:53:18,225 --> 00:53:19,225
では。
Well then.

699
00:53:19,425 --> 00:53:21,525
水がかり、ありがとう。
Thanks for the water.

700
00:53:22,225 --> 00:53:24,225
ラストウォーター。
Last water.

701
00:53:24,725 --> 00:53:28,225
センキュー、センキュー、センキュー。
Thank you, thank you, thank you.

702
00:53:28,725 --> 00:53:32,725
えっと、はい。では「夢見る空へ」です。
Uh, yes. Here is "Yumemiru Sora e".

703
00:53:32,825 --> 00:53:34,725
よろしくお願いします！
Please enjoy!

704
00:53:50,025 --> 00:53:54,725
重ねた手はギュッと離さずに
Holding tight our joined hands, never letting go

705
00:53:54,825 --> 00:53:55,725
行くよ
Here we go

706
00:53:57,725 --> 00:54:00,725
夢見る空へ
Towards the dreaming sky

707
00:53:57,725 --> 00:54:00,725
夢見る空へ
作詞・作曲・編曲：永塚健登
Towards the Dreaming Sky
Lyrics, Composition, Arrangement: Kento Nagatsuka

708
00:54:02,925 --> 00:54:07,725
最後だけど、みんな盛り上がっていこう！
It's the last one, so let's get hyped, everyone!

709
00:54:08,925 --> 00:54:11,825
窓越しに見上げた
Looking up through the window

710
00:54:11,825 --> 00:54:14,725
とても小さな空
At a very tiny sky

711
00:54:15,025 --> 00:54:17,425
ここで出会えたのは
What I encountered here

712
00:54:17,425 --> 00:54:19,725
数え切れない奇跡
Are countless miracles

713
00:54:19,925 --> 00:54:23,225
繰り返した一歩が
Each step repeated

714
00:54:23,225 --> 00:54:25,725
きらめきを繋いで
Connects the sparkles

715
00:54:25,925 --> 00:54:29,725
星のような笑顔導いた
Leading to a star-like smile

716
00:54:30,725 --> 00:54:35,725
Step by day みんなの声が力になる
Step by day, everyone's voices become my strength

717
00:54:35,725 --> 00:54:40,725
Step by stage ここでそれぞれ描くもの
Step by stage, what we each draw here

718
00:54:40,825 --> 00:54:43,225
それぞれ目指すもの
What we each aim for

719
00:54:43,225 --> 00:54:45,725
それぞれ願った夢
The dream each of us wished for

720
00:54:51,725 --> 00:54:56,725
重ねた手はギュッと離さずに
Holding tight our joined hands, never letting go

721
00:54:56,925 --> 00:54:59,925
一人一人違う色
Each and every person has a different color

722
00:54:59,925 --> 00:55:03,725
輝き出す時めき
A sparkle that begins to shine

723
00:55:03,683 --> 00:55:07,133
...そっと描く 真っ直ぐに
...softly drawing, straight ahead.

724
00:55:07,133 --> 00:55:08,233
行くよ！ (行こう！)
Here I go! (Let's go!)

725
00:55:08,233 --> 00:55:12,183
夢見る空へ
To the dreaming sky!

726
00:55:21,183 --> 00:55:26,083
笑い合ったことや つきそうにない話題
The things we laughed about, and topics that didn't seem to fit.

727
00:55:26,083 --> 00:55:31,083
思い出いっぱいなのに あっという間の日々
Even though they're full of memories, the days passed in a flash.

728
00:55:31,083 --> 00:55:36,083
上書きじゃなくて 名前付けて保存
Not overwriting them, but saving them with a name.

729
00:55:36,083 --> 00:55:41,183
どれも全部大事って 言いきれる
I can say for sure that every single one is important.

730
00:55:42,183 --> 00:55:47,083
One for All みんなのためが力になる
One for All, being there for everyone becomes my strength.

731
00:55:47,083 --> 00:55:52,083
All for One 今日も賑やかすぎるくらい
All for One, even today it's almost too lively.

732
00:55:52,083 --> 00:55:55,683
笑顔が止まらない
The smiles don't stop.

733
00:55:55,683 --> 00:56:00,183
思いは膨らんでいく
Our feelings keep on growing.

734
